{% comment %}
  In this case the Hero component was intentionally split into Desktop and Mobile
  versions.

  Since both layouts differ significantly in structure, positioning
  and styling, separating them results in simpler markup and more
  maintainable CSS than relying exclusively on responsive overrides.
{% endcomment %}
<section class="custom-hero">
  {% render 'custom-hero-desktop', section: section %}
  {% render 'custom-hero-mobile', section: section %}
</section>
